						</title>
						<text>
							Sperm whales don't have many predators. Giant squid, orcas, and great whites may prey on sperm whales, especially the young. There are many historical stories of deadly battles between sperm whales and giant squid, and sperm whales have even been seen with suction cup-shaped marks on their body.
